================================================================================
Backbone models and external perception models
================================================================================

Speech-Hands fine-tunes and evaluates against the following pretrained
artifacts. They are NOT redistributed in this repository; users are expected
to download them from their official hosts under each model's respective
license.

  * Qwen2.5-Omni-7B           — https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen2.5-Omni-7B
  * Parakeet-TDT-0.6B-v3      — https://huggingface.co/nvidia/parakeet-tdt-0.6b-v2
  * Whisper-v2-large          — https://huggingface.co/openai/whisper-large-v2
  * Canary-1B-v2              — https://huggingface.co/nvidia/canary-1b
  * Audio Flamingo 3          — https://huggingface.co/nvidia/audio-flamingo-3

================================================================================
Datasets
================================================================================

The paper evaluates on benchmarks whose audio and transcripts are governed by
their original licenses and distribution terms. Users are responsible for
obtaining them directly from the upstream sources:

  * AMI Meeting Corpus
  * TEDLIUM
  * GigaSpeech
  * SPGISpeech
  * VoxPopuli
  * LibriSpeech  (clean / other)
  * DCASE 2025 AudioQA Challenge
